description: This is the one you have been waiting for! Welcome to your new Southie condo that checks every box. This unit features gorgeous hardwood floors, central air, parking, a private entrance, ample storage and in-unit laundry. There are two bedrooms and two full bathrooms. The primary suite offers custom closets and a private outdoor space. You'll never have to search for parking again with a deeded parking spot out back. There is a private entrance into the unit from the front of the building. The location is ideal, close to the beach, Castle Island and local shops and restaurants. The warm and welcoming layout of this home paired with the A+ location is perfect for those who enjoy city living.
